Class HttpHeaders

java.lang.Object
com.google.common.net.HttpHeaders
@GwtCompatible public final class HttpHeaders extends Object
Contains constant definitions for the HTTP header field names. See:
  • RFC 2109
  • RFC 2183
  • RFC 2616
  • RFC 2965
  • RFC 5988
Since:
11.0
Author:
Kurt Alfred Kluever
